Rating: 4
This recipe was delicious! I'd definitely make it again. I made it for a function at work, and people raved about it. The shortbread was a little crumbly, and I had to use a very sharp knife to cut the bars. I also had a hard time spreading the coconut mixture over the shortbread base prior to baking it. The coconut mixture seemed a little hard when the cookies cooled and I prepared to cut them, but that wasn't a problem. The cookies were delicious. The recipe for the shortbread base has other recipes for bar cookies, and I'm eager to try them, too.

Rating: 3
